hopobject.body: What do you do for a living? vitalikor new formula reviews NOTES: The Orioles will activate Wei-Yin Chen (oblique strain) from the disabled list to start Wednesday night. Texas will counter with right-hander Josh Lindblom, who will be making his first start since June 20. ... Texas RHP Colby Lewis threw live batting practice Tuesday in his bid to return from offseason surgery on his right arm. "Overall, I felt great," Lewis said, although he acknowledged he needs to improve his arm strength. ... Beltre has six HRs in his last 11 games at Camden Yards.
